::Rex/Firearm::

Rex shakes his head, "I'm staying!" he says to Arcangel, turning his head 
back toward the Alliance base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm's gun arm twiches at Arcangels suggestion.

"Leave?!" he exclaims, "Ya kiddin'? And miss the chance to slag some bots?!"

"Shh!" Rex growls at Firearm, the other shutting up.
